%% Software agency stages — flowchart
flowchart LR
  classDef box fill:#f9f,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px;

  LG[Lead Generation\n- Content\n- Ads\n- Referrals]
  SL[Sales & Qualification\n- Outreach\n- Demos\n- Contracts]
  DS[Discovery\n- Research\n- Requirements\n- Scope]
  PR[Proposal & Pricing\n- Estimate\n- Terms]
  ON[Onboarding\n- Kickoff\n- Setup\n- Client Access]
  DSN[Design\n- UX/UI\n- Prototypes\n- Reviews]
  DEV[Development\n- Sprints\n- Code Reviews\n- Feature Work]
  QA[QA & Testing\n- Manual Tests\n- Automation\n- Acceptance]
  OPS[DevOps & Infra\n- CI/CD\n- Monitoring\n- Backups]
  LN[Launch\n- Release Plan\n- Handover]
  GM[Growth & Maintenance\n- Retainers\n- Optimization\n- Support]
  BL[Billing & Legal\n- Invoicing\n- Contracts\n- Compliance]

  LG --> SL --> DS --> PR --> ON --> DSN --> DEV --> QA --> OPS --> LN --> GM
  PR --> BL
  ON --> BL
  QA -->|Fixes| DEV
  GM -->|New leads/upsell| LG

  class LG,SL,DS,PR,ON,DSN,DEV,QA,OPS,LN,GM,BL box
